snippet: Energy prices mostly rose Friday as crude oil closed out the week with a 2 percent gain. Wheat and corn futures fell, while metals prices ended broadly higher....

headline.print_headline: Oil Ends the Week Higher; Wheat, Corn Prices Fall
headline.main: Oil Ends the Week Higher; Wheat, Corn Prices Fall

lead_paragraph: Energy prices mostly rose Friday as crude oil closed out the week with a 2 percent gain. Wheat and corn futures fell, while metals prices ended broadly higher.
